cross: Cattleya Okarchee x Laeliocattleya Miss Wonderful

measurements.description: Three full flowers on one upright 14-cm inflorescence; sepals lavender; petals full, crossing, ruffled edges, medium-dark lavender, white centrally proximally; lip frilly, dark lavender edges, dark lavender veins, yellow proximally, overlaid partially dark lavender veins; column white, dark lavender marks, anther cap white; substance firm; texture slightly crystalline.
